<reggrp_short_dscr>:
MAC address translation table
------------------------------
<reggrp_public_text>:
The MAC table contains MAC address translation configuration. It is indexed by ES0 action MAC_IDX

The table lookup is controlled by the REW_CMD received from the EACL block. The following commands are supported:

0: Default - no operation.
1: Swap MAC addresses. Clear bit 40 in new SMAC.
2: Translate the DMAC using VCAP_ES0 action.
3: Translate the SMAC using VCAP_ES0 action.
4-7: Reserved. Undefined at time of writing
